2. Apply It

Run:

oc apply -f sriov-network.yaml


---

3. Verify NAD Creation

Run:

oc get net-attach-def -n cnf

You MUST see:

bscf-bh0c_1-nad
bscf-bh0c_2-nad
bscf-bh0u_2_1-nad
...


---

4. Restart BIP Deployments

Run:

oc rollout restart deploy bscf5000-bip0 -n cnf

oc rollout restart deploy bscf5000-bip1 -n cnf


---

5. Watch Pods

Run:

oc get po -w

Expected:

pods created successfully

no FailedCreate

interfaces attached

containers start



